data.description: Motivated Seller! Welcome to the epitome of comfortable living! This meticulously designed residence boasts an array of features, including a grand entrance with tiled and screened entry, custom double doors, and a marble-tiled foyer. Enjoy the convenience of designer ceiling fans, ceramic tile baths and kitchen, and a great room with vaulted ceilings and solar tube. The bright kitchen features beveled edge counters, pantry, and recessed lighting, while the master suite offers Berber carpet, two walk-in closets, and a master bath with dual sinks and a walk-in shower. Additional highlights include a guest suite with a room-size walk-in closet, a Florida room with tiled flooring and glass sliding windows, and an attached 2-car garage. Outside, a 15x30 free-form patio with custom pavers invites you to enjoy the good life. Located in a friendly HOA maintained village, this home ensures a carefree lifestyle with no outside work required.
